*{{citation|title=none|first=Mary E.|last=Wells|journal=The American Mathematical Monthly|volume=25|issue=2|date=February 1918|pages=72–74|doi=10.2307/2971993}}
*{{citation|title=none|first=Philip E. B.|last=Jourdain|journal=Science Progress|volume=12|issue=48|date=April 1918|page=684|jstor=43426456}}
